[12Jul2026 05:52:25.865] [Server thread/INFO] [net.minecraft.server.MinecraftServer/]: Chunky Commands
chunky start - Start a new chunk generation task
chunky pause - Pause current tasks and save progress
chunky continue - Continue current or saved tasks
chunky cancel - Stop and delete current or saved tasks
chunky world <world> - Set the world target
chunky worldborder - Use the world border center & radius
chunky center <x> <z> - Set the center block location
chunky spawn - Set the center to the spawn point
chunky radius <radius> - Set the radius
chunky corners <x1> <z1> <x2> <z2> - Set by corners
chunky shape <shape> - Set the shape to generate
chunky pattern <pattern> - Set the generation pattern
chunky silent - Toggle displaying update messages
chunky quiet <interval> - Set the quiet interval
chunky trim - Delete chunks outside selection
chunky selection - Display the current selection
chunky progress - Displays current task progress
chunky reload - Reload configuration
